headline: 3 Reasons CAG is Risky and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: What a brutal six months it’s been for Conagra. The stock has dropped 20.3% and now trades at $21.60, rattling many shareholders. This was partly driven by its softer quarterly results and might have investors contemplating their next move.
